data.text:
UHF small round label RFID mini-label ISO18000-6C intelligent electronic labels passive stickers equiped with NXP UCODE 9. Its circular shape makes it very Easy & Quick to apply, especially when trying to align the label to the corner sides of the object, making it ideal for deployment across a multitude of applications.

Printer Support

ZEBRA: ZT400 Series, ZT600 Series, ZD500R, ZE500R, etc.

SATO: CT4-LX Series, CL4NX, CL4NX Plus, CL6NX Plus, S84-ex,etc.
